 if I had really lost, I would have wanted a lot. 

00:21:10.720 --> 00:21:15.760
 I would have looked after my ego, I would have shown humility. 

00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:23.120
 I knew from my own judgment where I screwed up or not. 

00:21:23.240 --> 00:21:26.560
 Trading Machines, the THF company of Haim Bodek ... 

