 10? - Less than 10 people. 

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:33.960
 Do you know them all? 

00:28:34.080 --> 00:28:39.640
 I know several of them personally, but not all. 

00:28:40.960 --> 00:28:44.120
 I know their work well. 

00:28:45.920 --> 00:28:50.400
 What was the function of the algorithms that you designed at Citadel? 

00:28:50.520 --> 00:28:53.040
 I can't tell you that. 

00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:55.720
 I'm really scared of Citadel lawyers. 

